---
// Full-width photographic band — a visual pause between sections.
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative h-[60vh] min-h-[420px] w-full">
    <video
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
      poster="/img/band-poster.webp"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <source src="/img/band.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy via-navy/75 to-navy/30"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy via-transparent to-navy/60"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex h-full max-w-7xl items-center px-5 sm:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p data-reveal class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-gold">Why GoldenPath</p>
        <h2 data-reveal style="--reveal-delay:80ms" class="font-display text-3xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.9rem]">
          Our essence isn't the warehouse —<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          it's the <span class="text-gold-gradient">people</span> who make it run.
        </h2>
        <p data-reveal style="--reveal-delay:160ms" class="mt-5 max-w-md text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
          We build human relationships rooted in trust and respect, opening real
          opportunities for hard-working people and reliable teams for the businesses
          that depend on them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
